  amd64 stable wrt bug #214622

  15 Feb 2008; Markus Dittrich <markusle@gentoo.org> orpie-1.4.3-r1.ebuild,
  orpie-1.5.1.ebuild:
  Fixed QA issues and added bindist for >=gsl-1.10 (see bug #199451).

